data.description: Well maintained and move in ready in the beautiful community of Summerfield! Low HOA, no CDD and tons of amenities are just a few of the reasons to call this home! This 3 bed 2 bath home features a traditional split floorplan with combined formal living and dining rooms, and an open kitchen / family room / breakfast nook area. Upon entering the foyer, your eyes are immediately drawn through the living/dining area to the natural light streaming in from the spacious screened lanai. This home is perfectly situated so that you can enjoy sunrise and sunset on your lanai without having the direct heat from the sun beating in. Contemporary wood look tile is throughout the home, making clean up and maintenance a breeze! Owner's suite includes huge walk in closet and ensuite bath with recently updated shower. The kitchen features an abundance of high quality wood cabinetry, granite countertops, stainless appliances and a brand new disposal. The large family room with stone fireplace is sure to be the gathering spot for family & friends. Secondary bedrooms are large, and share an updated hall bath. The expansive lanai and fully fenced backyard are perfect for BBQs, entertaining, your pups, or little ones. Recent upgrades include new gutters on the front of the house, new ceiling fans, new garbage disposal, new microwave and new pull down attic stairs. There are owned solar panels that operate the hot water heater only, providing you with energy savings. HVAC was replaced in 2015, and all ducts were cleaned and sanitized one year ago. As a bonus, there is an attached floor safe in the owner's walk-in closet that will stay with the home. The beautiful Summerfield community offers 2 pools, an indoor basketball gym, fitness rooms with weights, elliptical machines, stationary bikes, treadmills, tennis courts, a volleyball court, dog park, playground, pavilion and a new rental hall that can be rented out for special events. And pickleball courts are coming soon. Close to public transportation, VA clinics, restaurants, shopping and the interstate for commuting.
